*refind-0.10.2-r1 (25 Oct 2016)

  25 Oct 2016; Göktürk Yüksek <gokturk@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +refind-0.10.2-r1.ebuild:
  use flags and udk for rEFInd, bug #566930

  This new release has 2 major changes:
  * it is now using user defined flags, if possible,
  * it is now able to compile against udk (default compilation).

  25 Oct 2016; Göktürk Yüksek <gokturk@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  improve metadata

